Controversial actress Tonto Dikeh, has revealed what kept her with ex-lover, Prince Kpokpogri. The single mother shared this on her Instagram story after she shared a video of her ex-lover twerking recently. The video, in turn, elicited comments from her ex-lover and fans.   Grammy needs to create Afrobeats category, says Bankulli     Wizkid breaks silence after Grammy loss     Davido’s aide Isreal DMW proposes to girlfriend   Reacting to a post by a comment that insinuated she missed her ex-lover, she wrote: “The funniest comment I’ve seen today…’She Dey miss d pr***…..This is very laughable, even the owner knows there is nothing down there. Love and Lies kept me there!! Betrayal is what brought us here!” For a couple of months, Dikeh and Kpokpogri seemed to have ceased hostilities to concentrate on their individual lives until the actress renewed the biff.